(Corrects spelling of name in headline.)  Troika Dialog, the investment arm of
Russian lender OAO Sberbank, hired Dean Tyler as head of
international fixed-income sales, the company said in a
statement today.  Troika hired Tyler from Moscow-based competitor VTB
Capital, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
